data.description: Beautiful, spacious home on a beautiful lot. Priced according to recent comparables. This house has tons of room and natural light. Boasting many thousands of dollars of updates in the last 3 years including all NEW ROOF, LEAF FILTER GUTTERS, NEW HVAC, NEW GRANITE COUNTERS, NEW MASTER. ENSUITE, NEW PRIVACY FENCE. Enjoy BBQing with family & friends on your large concrete patio under the shade of a beautiful live oak tree. Plus a huge shed, metal gazebo and adorable playhouse convey!
